@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (v2 - wp.exp(tmp))
    tmp = 0.16
    v2 = wp.cos(((tmp + 0.45 + v0 + 0.87) + wp.sin(v2 + 0.57)))
    tmp = wp.exp(((v0 + 0.51 * tmp + 0.59) * wp.exp(v1 + 0.98)))
    data[tid] = v0
